.sp
For any \fI\%blob.blob()\fP object, \fIencoding\fP and \fIcase\fP, encodings via
the \fI\%xblob.encode()\fP method and the \fI\%blob.encode()\fP
function are equal:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
# Always true:
